OL,3,CMinister apologises 'unreservedly' as
OL,4,CLido tender proven to be unfair
OL,6,FJersey's Infrastructure Minister has
OL,7,Fapologised "sincerely and
OL,8,Funreservedly" after an independent
OL,9,Freview found the Havre Des Pas Lido
OL,10,Ftender process to be flawed.
OL,12,FThe community group 'Love Our Lido'
OL,13,Fwas named the preferred bidder to run
OL,14,Fthe business side of the popular
OL,15,Ffacility, including the cafe and
OL,16,Fevents space.
