OL,3,CMinister apologises 'unreservedly' as
OL,4,CLido tender proven to be unfair
OL,6,FWhile the report by Jurat Olsen found
OL,7,Fthat the initial phase of the
OL,8,F'expressions of interest' process was
OL,9,Ffair, it concluded that the group did
OL,10,Fnot withdraw from the process as
OL,11,Fstated by the Government - they were
OL,12,Fremoved from it.
OL,14,FConnetable Andy Jehan signed a
OL,15,FMinisterial Decision confirming the
OL,16,Fintention to appoint First Point, a
OL,17,Fproperty management company, to take
OL,18,Fover business operations - but now
OL,19,Fsays, in light of these findings, this
OL,20,Fwill be scrapped.
