OL,3,CMinister apologises 'unreservedly' as
OL,4,CLido tender proven to be unfair
OL,6,FConnetable Jehan explains: " I
OL,7,Fcategorically state that I did not
OL,8,Fintentionally or knowingly mislead the
OL,9,FAssembly and that I have acted in good
OL,10,Ffaith at all times.
OL,12,F"Following Jurat Olsen's findings, we
OL,13,Fwill re-run the second part of the
OL,14,Fprocess.
OL,16,F"I feel that this must be undertaken
OL,17,Fexternally to Jersey Property
OL,18,FHoldings. I have therefore asked
OL,19,FJersey Business to run and oversee
OL,20,Fthis process to a conclusion.
OL,26,@nD@Err
