OL,6,F"In the first instance, negotiations
OL,7,Fwill re-commence with Love Our Lido to
OL,8,Fseek to agree a lease by the end of
OL,9,FJanuary 2026.
OL,11,F"It is important to be clear that the
OL,12,Ffinancial terms on which an agreement
OL,13,Fis available to either party ` that of
OL,14,Fa #60,000 annual payment towards the
OL,15,Frunning and maintenance costs of the
OL,16,Fpremises (subject to annual RPI
OL,17,Fincreases) remains the offer available.
