OL,6,F"This was set out from the beginning
OL,7,Fof the process and, in the interests
OL,8,Fof fairness, no additional public
OL,9,Ffunding is available to either party."
OL,11,FThe site is run by Jersey Property
OL,12,FHoldings (JPH) on behalf of the
OL,13,FGovernment, which owns the entire
OL,14,Ffacility.
OL,16,FThis is a breaking news story. More to
OL,17,Ffollow.
